I visited Magident for toothache and it turned out that I have to go through root canal. I stay abroad so I wanted my root canal treatment to be completed with less number of sessions and with precision to avoid tooth pain in the flight or later.

Dr. Shetake and his staff is very professional and provided clear instructions during the procedure and explained what is being done to the tooth and what to expect. 

There was no pain or swelling during or after the root canal treatment.

I will definitely recommend Dr. Shetake for any tooth related issues.

I visited the clinic for severe toothache, on checking he found molar no.2 with a cavity and explained me options. When I was convinced I got myself prepared for root canal treatment. Entire procedure was carried out in 4 visits. I can now eat anything with my molar. Doctor is really trustworthy.

Had a wonderful experience with Dr. Girish. He explains everything in details, In depth information of the complete process and the accessories available. The prices are truly nomina and also he  gives us the genuine advice and not an advice to make money l, he frankly will advice you not to go for things that are not required. I will surely recommend him for anything in dental domain .

It was a very nice experience.. I have seen other dentists who just go for big treatments like root canal or tooth extraction even if it's not needed to earn money..however Dr. Girish has recommended just for cement filling and not root canal which I found really genuine.

I was apprehensive about going to a new dentist.
But after visiting Dr.Girish Shetake,I felt very comfortable due to his professional approach, a detailed clear explanation of the problem and solution,timeline and consequences .
There was punctuality and very approachable assistance too.
I was happy to find a good doctor and the treatment

* **** *** ** ****** ** ************ His method of treatment n explanation about the issue.. He makes patient comfortable...

Firstly we apologize if we have offended you in any sense. As I remember you were treated in our 90 feet road clinic setup. Due to current lockdown policies , we cannot give enough time to patient after 7pm . If patient has anatomical difficulties to work inside mouth ,we have to apply few barriers and suction to complete the treatment.  For this we prefer daytime appointment .As u could not manage your appointment during day time, it was difficult for us to give enough consoling time during night appointments. 
Anyways as we have completed the root canal treatment , you can continue your treatment with other dentist . You can contact anytime if you need any case records . We ll be happy to see you in future .
 Again we are sorry to find you on negative side of our feedback portal.
